{"tid":2400614,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"居深圳港人　經商務豁免後回港確診　39歲男子一家五口同染疫","createTime":"2021-02-09T05:54:44.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-09T06:23:29.000Z","uid":261647,"like":17,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"592164c1a1be40b911fb8ca4fb1d8d9a0c7fb547","tid":2400614,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T05:54:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2874251/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2874251%2F&d=%2BRZE95FanBIG1LNh2hoNMIkJ8G0wCzjK2GZdEgWvKr0%3D&h=aa0d9e3e\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2874251/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2870000/2874251/case01_thumb_20210208_K_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2870000%2F2874251%2Fcase01_thumb_20210208_K_1024.jpg&h=18f41a5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本港新冠肺炎疫情持續，早前一名39歲商務豁免人士抵港後發病並確診（個案編號：10581），居東涌映灣園悅濤軒3期9座，同行返港一名家人亦確診；而於映灣園悅濤軒3期9座同住的3名家人亦告確診。<br />\n<br />\n第10,581宗確診的39歲男子屬商務豁免人士，早前一直在深圳居住，1月21日曾做病毒測試呈陰性，1月23日由深圳抵港，1月30日開始感到頭痛，2月3日檢測後結果呈陽性。<br />\n<br />\n當時衞生防護中心傳染病處主任張竹君表示，暫列為本地個案。<br />\n<br />\n張竹君今日被問及有關個案時解釋，暫未能確定誰屬感染源頭。"},{"pid":"55458e1b738a882a7acdf9012c5cfd30f5761833","tid":2400614,"uid":155095,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T05:55:47.000Z","msg":"計入香港本地個案<br />\n<br />\n深圳係香港一部分"},{"pid":"23cffcdd97c77910281e92c6c0846a7759fafec9","tid":2400614,"uid":114781,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T05:56:51.000Z","msg":"衞生防護中心傳染病處主任張竹君表示，暫列為本地個案。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e99daa3ac44734ad71b669a9a06a69e6646af07b","tid":2400614,"uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T05:56:55.000Z","msg":"唔封關根本冇用"},{"pid":"c3f7d